response: JitStreamer will never support cellular networks. This is not a problem with JitStreamer, it’s a limitation of iOS. There is nothing we can do about it.

**Use this unregester shortcut if you are stuck on a error where you can’t click unregister the main shortcut. Make sure to be connected to the vpn when doing this.** https://www.icloud.com/shortcuts/31a67e5d75a94128943fedc739a91b27
